quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  81,1,"Amai ka so Alongan na kowa­an sa Sindao,"
  81,2,"Go amai ka so manga Bito-on na manga o olog,"
  81,3,"Go amai ka so manga Palao na Mamangikayontong,"
  81,4,"Go amai ka so manga Onta a maogat na indarainon,"
  81,5,"Go amai ka so manga Bina­tang na timo-on,"
  81,6,"Go amai ka so manga Kalo­dan na Pakakadugun,"
  81,7,"Go amai ka so manga Niyawa na ito-on ko manga ganap iyan."
  81,8,"Go amai ka so Bagowaraga a ini lubung a Oyagoyag na i isha,"
  81,9,"O antona-a i dosa a sabap a ini bono-on;"
  81,10,"Go amai ka so manga daptar (a siyoratan ko manga Amal) na kayatun,"
  81,11,"Go amai ka so Langit na pokasun ko darpa iyan,"
  81,12,"Go amai ka so Naraka Jahim na Pakashokhaya-on,"
  81,13,"Go amai ka so Sorga na ipakarani (ko Miyamananggila),"
  81,14,"Na katokawan o ginawa so Pithiyagar iyan."
  81,15,"Na Pushapa Ako sa lbut ko (manga Bito-on a) somubang so­mudup,"
  81,16,"A Puphamalalagoi a Pupha­mangigaib,"
  81,17,"Go so gagawi-i igira a pha­kalibotung,"
  81,18,"Go so khapita igira-a phaka­liwanag."
  81,19,"Mata-an! (a giya Qur-a n naya) na titho a gi-i Matharo o Sogo a Susula-an,"
  81,20,"Mabagur si-i ko khiruk ko Kapa-ar, a adun a Pangkatan Ni­yan,"
  81,21,"Pukhaonotan ro-o, a Kasasa­na-an."
  81,22,"Na da ko Bolayoka iyo (a Muhammad) iba Pumbuthanga."
  81,23,"Na Sabunsabunar a miyailai Niyan sukaniyan (a Jibril) ko sinda­dan o kailai sa porn a mapayag;"
  81,24,"Go kuna a ba Niyan ini pu­ligut so katawan Niyan ko dama­payag;"
  81,25,"Go kuna a ba aya Katharo a Shaitan a Puradiyamun:"
  81,26,"Na anda kano shong?"
  81,27,"Da-a salakao saya a rowar sa Pananadum a bagiyan o manga Ka­adun,"
  81,28,"Si-i ko tao a kabaya lyan rukano a kapakaontol iyan:"
  81,29,"Na da-a kapa-ar iyo, inonta sa kabaya o Allah, a Kadnan o manga Ka-adun."
